        "text": "## Result\n\n**No stability constants measured in supercritical CO₂ are available in the NIST SRD-46 database.**\n\nThe database's `solvent_name` field contains only **H₂O (water)** — all 79,063 measured stability constant records use water as the solvent. There are no entries for supercritical CO₂ (scCO₂), liquid CO₂, or any non-aqueous/mixed solvent system.",
